would be the scurf of yesterday's.

638
00:56:05,238 --> 00:56:06,405
Tickets, please.

639
00:56:10,493 --> 00:56:12,203
How's work?

640
00:56:13,538 --> 00:56:15,081
You asked me already.

641
00:56:18,834 --> 00:56:21,337
You OK these days?

642
00:56:21,420 --> 00:56:22,922
Pretty much.

643
00:56:24,257 --> 00:56:26,217
I feel a change.

644
00:56:30,096 --> 00:56:31,389
I had two heart attacks...

645
00:56:31,472 --> 00:56:34,725
an abortion,
did crack while I was pregnant.

646
00:56:36,644 --> 00:56:38,354
Other than that, I'm fine.

647
00:56:38,437 --> 00:56:40,064
Good.

648
00:56:43,859 --> 00:56:45,820
Something wrong?

649
00:56:48,614 --> 00:56:49,949
No, nothing.

650
00:56:51,742 --> 00:56:53,452
Your gnome's gone.

651
00:56:54,954 --> 00:56:57,248
Is he back in the toolshed?

652
00:57:10,344 --> 00:57:12,638
Moscow. There. See?

653
00:57:14,390 --> 00:57:16,642
No explanation.

654
00:57:17,643 --> 00:57:19,979
He wants to see the world?

655
00:57:23,107 --> 00:57:25,026
I can't understand it.

656
00:57:43,419 --> 00:57:44,170
LOST

657
00:57:44,253 --> 00:57:44,920
BAG

658
00:57:45,004 --> 00:57:45,671
PHOTOS

659
00:57:49,800 --> 00:57:53,095
<i>Any normal girl would call the number...</i>

660
00:57:53,179 --> 00:57:55,306
<i>meet him, return the album...</i>

661
00:57:55,389 --> 00:57:58,643
<i>and see if her dream is viable.</i>

662
00:57:58,726 --> 00:58:00,936
<i>It's called a reality check.</i>

663
00:58:01,020 --> 00:58:04,190
<i>The last thing Amélie wants.</i>

664
00:58:08,778 --> 00:58:09,987
I say!

665
00:58:10,071 --> 00:58:12,531
Could she be falling in love?

666
00:59:48,669 --> 00:59:50,212
Where's the boss?

667
00:59:51,630 --> 00:59:53,382
Sleeping in the cauliflower.

668
00:59:53,466 --> 00:59:57,595
- What?
- Sleeping in the cauliflower.

669
01:00:04,727 --> 01:00:06,729
You want me... want what?

670
01:00:06,812 --> 01:00:08,689
A scratchcard, please.

671
01:00:17,656 --> 01:00:19,325
How does it work?

672
01:00:21,827 --> 01:00:26,665
Tell you what.
Let's both do one together.

673
01:00:29,543 --> 01:00:32,713
You scratch it here...

674
01:00:32,797 --> 01:00:34,298
sideways.

675
01:00:44,183 --> 01:00:45,518
Nothing. You?

676
01:00:46,143 --> 01:00:47,353
Me neither.

677
01:00:51,023 --> 01:00:52,817
Unlucky at cards...

678
01:00:54,777 --> 01:00:56,654
So they say.

679
01:00:58,864 --> 01:01:01,367
I have to get back.

680
01:01:02,034 --> 01:01:04,036
Yes.

681
